data.description: Come see this wonderful home before it is gone! This lovely property has, what is technically a formal dining room, that would be perfect to be used as a 3rd bedroom, as it already has a closet, window and its in entryway. This ranch is perfect for someone who wants to customize it into their own unique property. It boasts a lovely large yard and a screened in carport. The hot water heater is brand new. Just minutes away from all of the hot spots in Durham! Full interior professional photos coming soon!
